trans-unit.source: Identifies the reason for a Terminal Services session change.
Determines whether the specified object is equal to the current session change description.
The return value is `false` if `obj` is not a <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> or if it is `null`.

Equality is determined by comparing the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> properties of the specified <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> structure to the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> properties of the current <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> structure.
The two structures are considered equal if their properties are equal.
The object to compare to the current <xref href="System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription"></xref> structure.
if obj is equal to the current structure; otherwise, .
Determines whether the specified session change description is equal to the current session change description.

Equality is determined by comparing the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> properties of the specified <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> structure to the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> properties of the current <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> structure.
The two structures are considered equal if their properties are equal.

Gets a hash code for the current session change description.

The returned hash code is calculated from the values of the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> properties.
The hash code should not be used to compare <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> instances.
A hash code for the current session change description.
